19:04.121 --> 19:06.226
<i>You're doing it wrong.
You're making a girl angel.</i>

19:06.227 --> 19:07.829
You should make a boy angel.

19:07.830 --> 19:09.997
There's no such thing
as a boy snow angel.

19:09.998 --> 19:11.223
Snow angels are unisex.

19:11.224 --> 19:12.797
Unisex? That doesn't make sense.

19:12.798 --> 19:15.224
Hey, man, he's still raw.

19:15.225 --> 19:16.778
Let him be.

19:24.175 --> 19:25.852
I think it looks really nice.

19:25.853 --> 19:27.790
Yeah. Better than I thought.

19:29.531 --> 19:31.354
I see you wrapped the presents.

19:31.355 --> 19:32.482
[Sighs]

19:32.483 --> 19:35.531
Mike, I know it was an
unconventional Christmas,

19:35.532 --> 19:38.395
but I got to say,
I really enjoyed it.

19:38.396 --> 19:40.668
Yeah, well, you needed a break.

19:40.669 --> 19:42.815
<i>I'm just happy to see you happy.</i>

19:42.816 --> 19:45.217
Aww. If there was
mistletoe up, I'd kiss you.

19:45.218 --> 19:47.884
- Mm.
- [Sighs]

19:47.885 --> 19:50.625
It's funny... for me, I always kind
of enjoyed all the Christmas stuff.

19:50.626 --> 19:51.453
Hmm.

19:51.454 --> 19:53.645
Didn't really get that
in my house growing up.

19:53.997 --> 19:57.364
I mean, after my mom died,
it was just a bunch of guys.

19:57.365 --> 19:58.456
Nobody was gonna decorate.

19:58.457 --> 19:59.590
[Chuckles lightly]

20:00.153 --> 20:01.815
In fact...

20:01.816 --> 20:05.655
I didn't really ever celebrate
Christmas until I met you.

20:08.121 --> 20:11.122
Anyway, I'm sure the
kids will be up early.

20:11.123 --> 20:12.005
I'm gonna go to bed.

20:12.006 --> 20:12.988
Mwah.

20:16.273 --> 20:18.431
Aw, crap.

20:20.365 --> 20:21.217
[Sighs]

20:30.350 --> 20:31.598
Oh, my God.

20:31.599 --> 20:33.531
It's Christmas!

20:33.532 --> 20:36.687
<i>Look! Look! The tree
It's pink and green!</i>

20:36.688 --> 20:38.623
Oh, my God. This is amazing!

20:38.624 --> 20:39.845
Mom!

20:39.846 --> 20:41.493
Oh, you got us so good!

20:41.494 --> 20:42.994
[Chkles]

20:43.755 --> 20:46.249
Hello, Mr. Mailman.

20:46.250 --> 20:47.778
Meet Miss Ice Skater.

20:47.779 --> 20:49.472
[Gasps] Have you got
a package for her?

20:50.951 --> 20:54.042
Yes! "Infinite Jest"!
I wanted this!

21:05.561 --> 21:08.942
<i>Frickin' Christmas...
It's so awesome.</i>

21:08.943 --> 21:10.901
<i>It really is the best holiday.</i>

21:10.902 --> 21:12.791
<i>Every time you think you're out,</i>

21:12.792 --> 21:14.834
<i>it just sucks you back in.</i>

21:14.835 --> 21:16.192
Who wants cocoa?

21:16.193 --> 21:17.001
- I do!
- Me!

21:17.002 --> 21:17.879
Right here!

